_json.title: An Alternative Way To House Quails For A Backyard Hobbyist.
_json.gridTitle: An Alternative Way To House Quails For A Backyard Hobbyist.
_json.description: What does a healthy deep litter system look like?  One thing for sure it should not stink!  Some tips to get you started:  -this system works for quails and chickens  -quails my need a little bit of help stirring up the bedding  -teach your quails how to scratch and forage for bugs  -manure will compost in your cage or aviary if you have a balanced microbe level -a healthier system and much less work in the long run  -it is kinder on your birds feet
